description:
White Springs: Accurate hourly data on the upper Suwannee River.

Do you enjoy spending time on the water, and live in (or near) north Florida? Rely on White Springs for river information about the upper Suwannee River. This skill will give you the current feet above sea level, and will let you know whether the river is dropping or rising. It also gives advice on current canoeing conditions. Information source: USGS.gov

"Alexa, ask White Springs..."

...about the Suwannee River.
...should i hit the river?
...should i go canoeing?
...how's the river?
...how many feet above sea level?
...what is the height of the suwannee river?
...what's the current info?
...for the current data.
...for a status update.
...about the depth.
...for recommendations.
...about canoeing advice.
...is it a good time to go canoeing?
...is the river flooding?
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask White Springs should i canoe the river?
Alexa, ask White Springs what is the current reading?
Alexa, ask White Springs for an update.
